---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Keshet Ranch"
  description="Privacy policy for Keshet Ranch website"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
>
  <Header lang="en" />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-earth-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-earth max-w-none space-y-6 text-earth-700 leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Keshet Ranch ("the Organization", "we") is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information, in compliance with the Israeli Protection of Privacy Law, 5741-1981, and the Privacy Protection Regulations (Data Security), 5777-2017.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">2. What Information Do We Collect?</h2>
          <p>Through the contact form on our website, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number (optional)</li>
            <li>Area of interest (joining, volunteering, donating, partnership)</li>
            <li>Free-text message</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong>Important:</strong> We recommend not including sensitive medical information in the free-text message. For discussions regarding medical or therapeutic matters, please contact us by phone.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">3. How Do We Use Your Information?</h2>
          <p>Your information will be used solely for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Responding to your inquiry</li>
            <li>Providing information about the ranch's programs</li>
            <li>Coordinating visits or program enrollment</li>
            <li>Sending updates about ranch activities (only if requested)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We will never sell, rent, or transfer your information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">4. How Do We Protect Your Information?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Encryption in transit:</strong> All data is transmitted via encrypted HTTPS connections.</li>
            <li><strong>No server-side storage:</strong> Form submissions are forwarded directly to our email and are not stored on website servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Restricted access:</strong> Only authorized ranch staff can access inquiries.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Inquiries are kept in our email as long as they are relevant to processing your request. After that, they are deleted. If your details are transferred to our donor/contact management system (CRM), they will be retained in accordance with legal requirements and our organizational policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under the Israeli Protection of Privacy Law, you have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Right of access:</strong> Request to see the information we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Right of correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate information.</li>
            <li><strong>Right of deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your information from our systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Right to object:</strong> Object to the use of your information for direct mailing.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, please contact us by email.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            This website does not use tracking cookies or analytics. We do not track your browsing activity.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900 mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about this privacy policy or requests regarding your data, please contact us:
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <strong>Keshet Ranch</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:info@keshetranch.com" class="text-terracotta underline">info@keshetranch.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
